title: Mathilde Panot - Wikipedia
snippet: Mathilde Françoise Panot (French pronunciation: [matild pano]; born 15 January 1989) is a French politician who has served as the president of the La France Insoumise group in the National Assembly since October 2021.

title: Mathilde Panot - La France insoumise
snippet: Mathilde Panot est député de la 10e circonscription du Val-de-Marne. Elle est membre de la commission du développement durable et de l'aménagement du territoire.
